# in.word — the sense. Axiom: bottoms out in the host (the in-crossing — the host hands the
# Word a word it did not make: another's word on the wire, the clock's reading, the lot's draw).
# Descends from word.word, base.word.

An in is made of the host.

An in takes a word the I_AM did not make.
The world hands it: another's word, the clock's reading, the lot's draw.

What comes in is content, never order.
